會加入戰團同更加死守<br />\n多過會做逃兵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知點解咁覺得<br />\n<br />\nbtw依家覺得呢世人最遺憾嘅就係冇好好讀書<br />\n做唔到中大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fbd0d4ae916ba47d3702739db6330ec0dccc08","tid":1715692,"uid":119908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:12:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79d614e66ea9c1a9435f0ec4fe3b52a0e7af8fbc","tid":1715692,"uid":161430,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"對家開始冇招 &gt; 上連登做散水黨<br />\n對家發覺自己會打輸 &gt; 出洗白文講大家係時候靜落黎 諗下咁樣對香港有月用 / 其實都有白警"},{"pid":"edd44c888448009b138fceab6ec98d8485eff3d0","tid":1715692,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:13:08.000Z","msg":"中大必守"},{"pid":"be9c16639a3e0f5bd537c49dd08fa769cf5d7996","tid":1715692,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d259a3707cf88c6abca8a3ea239a10c77868a6","tid":1715692,"uid":251119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e9fe571f5579e657d80d13413a65f0b8a1070629","tid":1715692,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:15:09.000Z","msg":"大量五毛叫人散水撤先<br />\n出架直升機就嚇到返屋企,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162e4b583a3a0fd3a5a8b09d2e96970f0d4b8621","tid":1715692,"uid":303722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:15:13.000Z","msg":"推呀上次禁蒙面法之後又係出左一大班散水撚休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d460bce275b7615d